Package edu.odu.cs.cs350.acmClassifier

Class Librarian

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.odu.cs.cs350.acmClassifier.Librarian
  • public class Librarian
extends Object
    The Librarian functions to implement training data acquired through the learningMachine. This class is the interface with which the user should run the train and classify programs. Whereas the learningMachine generates raw training data, the Librarian should be capable of examining this data and presenting it to the user, as well as interfacing with the learningMachine to interpret user input into training or classification.
